Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.cards

Class CardsFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.model.cards.CardsFactory
  • public class CardsFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    This cards generates the default set of cards that the game is played with. It features methods that generate the 3 different type cards when called (ammo, power up, weapon).

      • buildPowerUps

        private static void buildPowerUps()
        Generates the default list of power up cards based on the original rules of the game. 2 copies of each power up card are generated for each ammo color.

      • buildAmmo

        private static void buildAmmo()
        Generates the default list of ammo cards based on the original rules of the game. 3 copies of each ammo card are generated.

      • buildWeapons

        private static void buildWeapons()
        Generates the default list of weapon cards based on the original rules of the game. Every weapon has a unique function (or more than one) associated to it.
